Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:07.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H323F80&\blur1.5}いつかの空に導かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:12.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}２つの想いを一つずつ形にして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:16.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}奇跡を…もっと　超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:21.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H44ACC3&\blur1.5}君が描いた未来の世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:26.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H4697D0&\blur1.5}今もどこかで生き続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:34.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,450)\3c&H4197E8&\blur1.5}どんな夢重ねて　偽ることのないあの光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:37.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\3c&HB1601B&\blur1.5}Ah… Oh Keep me for my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:21.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,80)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5}一直 在光芒之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5}昨天還並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.95,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5}跟隨我腳步的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:34.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5\bord1.5}看不到終點的迷宮 被雨淋濕的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:38.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5\bord1.5}雖然沒有什麼後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:41.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,323)\3c&HF3A42D&\blur1.5}叫喊的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:46.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,323)\3c&H7094CA&\blur1.5}一定會傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:53.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&HBF9D8F&\blur1.5}在宣告這個故事開始的鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:57.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,250)\3c&HBF9D8F&\blur1.5}所連接的旅途之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:02.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H295DBC&\blur1.5}你所描繪的未來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:07.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H323F80&\blur1.5}被指引到曾幾何時的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:12.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}將兩份願望逐一化為有形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:16.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}將奇跡 不斷超越
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:21.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H44ACC3&\blur1.5}你所描繪的未來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:26.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H4697D0&\blur1.5}現在也在哪裏存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:34.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,450)\3c&H4197E8&\blur1.5}將那無論承載多少夢想 絕無虛偽的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:37.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\3c&HB1601B&\blur1.5}Ah… Oh 一直做我自己
